<view class="page">
  <view class="hero">
    <text class="title">MC 音效设置</text>
    <text class="desc">管理计分盘音效、外设快捷键和微信文件导入。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <text class="section-title">基础开关</text>
    <view class="switch-row">
      <view><text>2分音效</text><text class="hint">关闭后，加 2 分不再播放音效。</text></view>
      <switch checked="{{settings.twoEnabled}}" data-key="twoEnabled" bindchange="toggleSetting" />
    </view>
    <view class="switch-row">
      <view><text>3分音效</text><text class="hint">关闭后，长按 3 分不再播放音效。</text></view>
      <switch checked="{{settings.threeEnabled}}" data-key="threeEnabled" bindchange="toggleSetting" />
    </view>
    <view class="switch-row">
      <view><text>本机音效串联</text><text class="hint">开启后优先播放你导入的微信文件音效；没有导入时使用云端音乐库。</text></view>
      <switch checked="{{settings.localAudioEnabled}}" data-key="localAudioEnabled" bindchange="toggleSetting" />
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="section-head">
      <text class="section-title inline-title">音效类型与播放策略</text>
      <view class="refresh-btn" bindtap="loadCloudAudioLibrary">刷新云端</view>
    </view>
    <text class="hint import-tip">微信小程序不能直接读取手机音乐文件夹。个人音效需从微信聊天文件、文件传输助手或最近文件中选择；统一音乐建议在后台上传到云端音乐库。</text>
    <view wx:for="{{categories}}" wx:key="key" class="category-row">
      <view class="cat-main">
        <view class="cat-top">
          <view class="cat-copy">
            <text class="cat-name">{{item.label}}</text>
            <text class="hint">{{item.hint}}</text>
            <text wx:if="{{!item.isVoice}}" class="local-text">{{item.localText}}</text>
          </view>
          <view class="cat-tools">
            <view wx:if="{{item.isVoice}}" class="voice-package-list">
              <view wx:for="{{voicePackageOptions}}" wx:for-item="voice" wx:key="id" class="voice-package {{voice.activeClass}}" data-id="{{voice.id}}" bindtap="setVoiceStyle">{{voice.name}}</view>
            </view>
            <view wx:elif="{{item.hasMode}}" class="seg">
              <view class="seg-btn {{item.randomClass}}" data-key="{{item.key}}" data-mode="random" bindtap="setMode">随机</view>
              <view class="seg-btn {{item.fixedClass}}" data-key="{{item.key}}" data-mode="fixed" bindtap="setMode">固定</view>
            </view>
            <view wx:if="{{!item.isVoice}}" class="local-actions">
              <view class="local-btn" data-key="{{item.key}}" bindtap="importLocalAudio">微信文件导入</view>
              <view wx:if="{{item.localCount}}" class="clear-btn" data-key="{{item.key}}" bindtap="clearLocalAudio">清除</view>
            </view>
          </view>
        </view>

        <view wx:if="{{!item.isVoice}}" class="audio-panel">
          <text class="current-text">{{item.currentAudioText}}</text>
          <view wx:if="{{item.hasAudioItems}}" class="audio-list">
            <view wx:for="{{item.audioItems}}" wx:for-item="audio" wx:key="id" class="audio-item {{audio.currentClass}}">
              <text class="source-tag {{audio.sourceClass}}">{{audio.sourceText}}</text>
              <text wx:if="{{audio.channelText}}" class="channel-tag">{{audio.channelText}}</text>
              <text class="audio-name">{{audio.name}}</text>
              <text wx:if="{{audio.currentText}}" class="current-tag">{{audio.currentText}}</text>
            </view>
            <text wx:if="{{item.audioMoreText}}" class="audio-more">{{item.audioMoreText}}</text>
          </view>
          <text wx:else class="audio-empty">暂无音频。可以先从微信文件导入，或在 PC 后台把音乐保存到云端音乐库。</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <text class="section-title">外设快捷键设置</text>
    <text class="hint block">点击下方键位可替换外设触发的音效；具体键值请在计分盘右侧外设快捷键里点“监听”后绑定。</text>
    <view class="slot-grid">
      <view wx:for="{{quickSlots}}" wx:key="id" class="slot" data-id="{{item.id}}" bindtap="editSlot">
        <text class="slot-key">{{item.key}}</text>
        <text>{{item.label}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view wx:if="{{editingSlotId}}" class="action-sheet">
      <view wx:for="{{actionOptions}}" wx:key="key" class="action-option" data-action="{{item.key}}" bindtap="chooseSlotAction">{{item.label}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="primary" bindtap="saveSettings">保存设置</view>
</view>
